            <h2>NeuroML <%=nml2_version%> </h2>
            <br/>
            <p>The latest version of NeuroML is <b><%=nml2_version%></b>. The structure of NeuroML <%=nml2_version%> is defined by a
                single <a href="http://www.w3schools.com/schema/default.asp">XML Schema</a> file:
                <a href="https://github.com/NeuroML/NeuroML2/blob/master/Schemas/NeuroML2/NeuroML_<%=nml2_version%>.xsd">NeuroML_<%=nml2_version%>.xsd</a>.
                This should be the target structure for anyone wishing to implement NeuroML 2 support in their application.</p>



            <p align="center"><img alt="NeuroML <%=nml2_version%> structure" src="images/Figure6a.png" usemap="#NeuroMLstructure"/>
                <map name="NeuroMLstructure" id="NeuroMLstructure" >
